Author information:
(1)a a Mapi , Stockholm , Sweden.
(2)b b Karolinska University Hospital, Department of Medicine , Stockholm , 
Sweden.
(3)c c Medtronic Ltd , Watford , UK.
(4)d d Medtronic BioPharma BV , Heerlen , Netherlands.
(5)e e Norwich Medical School, University of East Anglia , Norwich , Norfolk , 
UK.
(6)f f Nottingham University Hospital, Centre for Spinal Studies and Surgery , 
Nottingham , UK.
(7)g g Oxford University Hospitals NHS Trust and Nuffield Department of 
