The Epidemiologic and Economic Impact of Improving HIV Testing, Linkage, and 
Retention in Care in the United States.

Shah M(1), Risher K(2), Berry SA(1), Dowdy DW(2).

Author information:
(1)Johns Hopkins University School of Medicine.
